{"tid":956670,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] 香港Warframe Discord Group 上線啦","createTime":"2018-12-26T12:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T13:02:04.000Z","uid":55657,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a74fe16a0717ebd402c6fe0fc3ec2ee4dc45523","tid":956670,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"本群以PC作為主要平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身群內都有一定人數<br />\n歡迎<span style=\"color: red;\">新手</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">老手</span> 加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地群有好大量資源可以比<span style=\"color: red;\">新手</span>參考吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋好多老手都好樂意幫吓新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入嚟就有你著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vac6FyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVac6FyP.jpg&h=5c83f920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJgLbHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJgLbHq.jpg&h=72ea0354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYZEf9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYZEf9j.jpg&h=0a36a153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsuQnPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsuQnPQ.jpg&h=54a21de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgPpsgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgPpsgG.jpg&h=082cca66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">老手</span>既話 呢度可以搵人組隊一齊farm嘢 打夜靈 蜘蛛 打埋飛機都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n最緊要多啲上水就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事不宜遲 link奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://discordapp.com/invite/QE2amd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2Finvite%2FQE2amd4&d=PU72c7fMpcCXWV7VN8abOgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=57f2c2f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/invite/QE2amd4</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意</span></span></strong> 請大家入群嘅時候 先到左上角下拉選單 隨以下格式更改暱稱 :<br />\n &quot;( your nick name) / ( warframe id)&quot;, <br />\ne.g : ABC / abc123456<br />\n返正聖誕毒撚一個都無地方去 入嚟一齊玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上本群吉祥物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRMCNc6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRMCNc6.gif&h=1c6262ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"678c113947f8e8971cacb41c4bf22741ebffed69","tid":956670,"uid":55657,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d034c0d7d1671166b0c2d2898cf951f09e7aa661","tid":956670,"uid":55657,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df31a8568d9ece78c32943433741fe7b8ed81206","tid":956670,"uid":55657,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a76d8cb5060